.TH GRAFANA-UTIL-DASHBOARD-IMPACT 1 "2026-04-03" "grafana-util 0.7.4" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-dashboard\-impact \- Estimate the blast radius of one datasource from dashboard governance artifacts.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util dashboard impact [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Estimate the blast radius of one datasource from dashboard governance artifacts.
.PP
Use this when you are about to change, migrate, or troubleshoot one datasource and need to know which dashboards and alert resources depend on it before you touch the live system.
.SH COMMON OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-governance
dashboard governance JSON input.
.TP
.B \-\-datasource\-uid
datasource UID to trace.
.TP
.B \-\-alert\-contract
optional alert contract JSON input.
.TP
.B \-\-output\-format
render text or json.
.TP
.B \-\-interactive
open the interactive terminal browser.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Estimate the blast radius of one datasource from dashboard governance artifacts.
.EX
grafana-util dashboard impact \
.EE
.PP
Estimate the blast radius of one datasource from dashboard governance artifacts.
.EX
  --governance ./governance.json \
.EE
.PP
Estimate the blast radius of one datasource from dashboard governance artifacts.
.EX
  --datasource-uid prom-main \
.EE
.PP
Estimate the blast radius of one datasource from dashboard governance artifacts.
.EX
  --output-format text
.EE
.SH SEE ALSO
\fBgrafana-util\fR(1)
